title: Just Petz Biodegradable Dog Poop Bags, 540 Count – Extra Thick & Leak-Proof, Lavender Scented, Eco Friendly, Fits All Dispensers, Durable Waste Bags for Small to Large Breeds
features: Lavender Scented to Neutralise Unpleasant Odours: Each bag is lightly infused with a soothing lavender fragrance that helps mask the smell of dog waste, creating a fresher, more pleasant clean-up experience. No more holding your breath—these scented bags make the task of picking up after your pet quicker, cleaner and more bearable. Ideal for daily use at home, in parks, or while travelling.

Eco-Conscious Materials – Reduce Plastic Waste Responsibly: Made using post-consumer recycled plastic, our bags offer an eco-friendlier choice for dog owners who care about the environment. They help reduce single-use plastic without sacrificing durability or functionality. A smart, sustainable alternative that fits your lifestyle while contributing to a cleaner planet for future generations.

Excellent Value – 540 Durable Bags in 36 Compact Rolls: Stay fully stocked for months with 540 strong dog poo bags neatly rolled into 36 easy-to-carry packs. Compatible with most standard bag dispensers, they’re ideal for dog owners who want practicality without waste. Perfect for homes with one or multiple pets, offering long-term savings and peace of mind on every walk or trip.

Large Bag Size for Easy Tie & Disposal – Fits All Breeds: Measuring a generous 320mm x 230mm, these waste bags offer plenty of space to handle any size mess. Whether you have a small puppy or a giant breed, you’ll have enough room to tie securely and dispose of waste with confidence. Easy to open, separate and use—even with gloves or in cold weather. No more messy accidents.
